{"tid":195043,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人活在夢中？","createTime":"2017-04-10T11:12:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-11T14:06:03.000Z","uid":50952,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"feebb79e78c4f2257c12a18e94899d5513021d45","tid":195043,"uid":50952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T11:12:15.000Z","msg":"Sorry第一次開post 唔知開係咩台。<br />\n<br />\n話說我好細個就好常發惡夢，而發惡夢嘅次數好頻密，講緊係一星期兩三次。<br />\n細細個發既都比較輕微，嚇醒好快會訓番，但最近四年好似越黎越嚴重。<br />\n岩岩開始嘅時候，我會夢到自己比人殺死，比人追殺，而殺我嘅人有時會我好親密嘅朋友或家人。而當我醒番嘅時候，我受傷/致命傷口係會痛，而我係好肯定冇嘢咬我或任何外來嘅刺激。<br />\n後來我發嘅夢越黎越長，時間線係以年為單位。<br />\n我會係夢中有完全唔同嘅人生，最長我試過過左5年。<br />\n而當我做完呢啲以恐怖終結嘅夢，我會嚇醒，然後精神會開始錯亂。<br />\n所謂嘅精神錯亂，即係我好似真係冇左五年。尋晚發生嘅事好似好耐以前嘅事，我會記得，但冇左切實嘅感覺。<br />\n到左最近一年，係我最嚴重嘅時候。我嘅夢除左長，仲有好多嘅連貫性。我指嘅連貫性除左指佢真係好似一段真嘅人生之外，仲同我現實極度相似。我會夢到我最好嘅朋友變左殺人犯，我屋企前面座山要撞過黎等等。以前雖然都會嚇醒，但甚少會半夜醒。但最近差唔多發親都醒，醒左我會極度恐懼，都開番燈我先可以慢慢入睡。<br />\n而最恐怖，係夢入面有兩個我。一個我係我自我意識，第二個「我」係夢入面嘅自我。「我」一直想捉走我，拉我入去好黑嘅地方，例如房，或冇人嘅街道。我有時會失去左身體嘅控制權，知道發生咩事但好似比人吞噬左。而「我」好似真係想我消失。<br />\n我醒番嘅感覺真係好似比人拎走左嘢，自我意識好唔穩。<br />\n而呢八年入面，我一直好少分得出現實同夢境，呢點亦我極度痛苦....<br />\n<br />\n我同過幾個人傾過呢個問題，佢地會覺得好好笑，好好玩，同好誇張。<br />\n但真係好可怕，我甚至連平時都會有恐懼，諗到訓教雖然真係好攰好想訓，但又想再發惡夢，最驚會醒番已經唔係我，而係比「我」控制住。<br />\n後遺症係我成日會失神，大腦成日空白（朋友家人話）<br />\n我真係好痛苦，到底可以點擺脫？<br />\n<br />\n多謝睇到呢度嘅你哋。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1e8ad48e018d0cb024461e370464f30dc9440e4","tid":195043,"uid":50952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T11:19:32.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d24ebd246735bdcf6454779557f29f8c87667e7a","tid":195043,"uid":50952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T11:21:27.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cdc47acb751189daa7cc5ae81713fdc205007c1","tid":195043,"uid":50952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T11:24:42.000Z","msg":"Pish <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97b6b481b9535275030e56e5fec106372d2275a5","tid":195043,"uid":21899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T11:24:58.000Z","msg":"咁樓主喺夢入面控制到幾多嘢？"},{"pid":"09c1311bbf6e4275dc147856915455b8f4f57200","tid":195043,"uid":50952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T11:29:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁樓主喺夢入面控制到幾多嘢？</blockquote><br />\n多謝巴打回我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我係夢入面係另一個人生，係最近「我」出現之前我可以控制大部分嘅事，例如做下一啲決定"},{"pid":"7a42d49e39fc8736506b5a0495499046a3c51f04","tid":195043,"uid":24948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T11:32:07.000Z","msg":"精神分裂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acbd0073e04f26e2d2663f507c369d6a37aa1896","tid":195043,"uid":78243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T11:33:43.000Z","msg":"要睇心理醫生"},{"pid":"298b3e08d2a38fc3bc306f1335f0f3650607ad87","tid":195043,"uid":50952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T11:36:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>精神分裂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 多謝巴打回覆<br />\n<br />\n其實我好耐之前都會諗過呢個問題，唔否認有呢個可能性。我已經諗唔起細個發生過嘅事，就算有都係好痛苦嘅回憶....即係話如果真係分裂，即係我好細個已經訓左？咁而家啲我係唔係我....？"},{"pid":"3133b6e0e2ee879ee8c449fae6faadca94b567e3","tid":195043,"uid":50952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T11:38:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>要睇心理醫生</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 多謝巴打回覆<br />\n<br />\n其實我會外熱內冷嘅一個人，自己有咩事都唔會講，上嚟開post可能會極限...但真係好驚失去自己。"},{"pid":"4428a45dcaf97b74fcb8f45c75f1564d45ddc9d6","tid":195043,"uid":24948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T11:44:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>要睇心理醫生</blockquote><br />\n加一"},{"pid":"e1cb724449fa1709d41aef81cc4f899c534943a9","tid":195043,"uid":50952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T11:45:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>要睇心理醫生</blockquote><br />\n加一</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d37d878066c60e79df260619337f1d81e17c1363","tid":195043,"uid":24948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T13:04:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>要睇心理醫生</blockquote><br />\n加一</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n幫唔到你 唯有祝福你可以無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"434992a49d452d2870c1db3252bcabe57ebbc57f","tid":195043,"uid":32877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T13:05:31.000Z","msg":"真係要睇 我都會俾夢困擾 不過情況輕微好多好多"},{"pid":"066e8ab1b7b82947d496a0f85a19ed39085e0ba0","tid":195043,"uid":50952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T13:25:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>要睇心理醫生</blockquote><br />\n加一</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n幫唔到你 唯有祝福你可以無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n多謝巴打<br />\n而家我成日都好壓抑"},{"pid":"4d181723351434da0fcd8982a693ac2da7739674","tid":195043,"uid":50952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T13:25:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>真係要睇 我都會俾夢困擾 不過情況輕微好多好多</blockquote><br />\n巴打睇醫生好番？"},{"pid":"5789f6db228abca34a755178c46c5b8ce607b784","tid":195043,"uid":21899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T13:31:35.000Z","msg":"樓主細個有啲唔係咁好嘅經歷？"},{"pid":"3fc5260dc39d41ee974a9572a67ae6e6b068063f","tid":195043,"uid":82481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T13:36:42.000Z","msg":"我最近呢一年都成日發夢，睡眠質素都好差，訓幾個鍾又醒下，又發夢<br />\n我自己覺得發夢好爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好似有兩次人生咁<br />\n但就愈訓愈少，跟住開始失眠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後睇完中醫後睡眠質素好左好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望樓主有早日好返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11d0d89b5dbac3fe59a12e1b0a1f148e749fe0c1","tid":195043,"uid":50952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T13:40:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主細個有啲唔係咁好嘅經歷？</blockquote><br />\n的確係有唔快樂嘅童年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff2c0585466a49fce28f662c49b248aa7aaa81cb","tid":195043,"uid":50952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T13:43:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我最近呢一年都成日發夢，睡眠質素都好差，訓幾個鍾又醒下，又發夢<br />\n我自己覺得發夢好爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好似有兩次人生咁<br />\n但就愈訓愈少，跟住開始失眠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後睇完中醫後睡眠質素好左好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望樓主有早日好返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我從好細個已經係咁，細細個已經唔覺得快樂，因為都係好恐怖既內容。而家大左更加冇「爽」嘅感覺，有好夢就好似中左六合彩咁，好辛苦。<br />\n因為實際上好難形容比人聽，講左人地又覺得好誇張，令我慢慢唔想同人講&hellip;&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7cfd9ea70c791a348ddc5c82cd411f3e64a1a3b","tid":195043,"uid":82481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T13:49:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我最近呢一年都成日發夢，睡眠質素都好差，訓幾個鍾又醒下，又發夢<br />\n我自己覺得發夢好爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好似有兩次人生咁<br />\n但就愈訓愈少，跟住開始失眠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後睇完中醫後睡眠質素好左好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望樓主有早日好返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我從好細個已經係咁，細細個已經唔覺得快樂，因為都係好恐怖既內容。而家大左更加冇「爽」嘅感覺，有好夢就好似中左六合彩咁，好辛苦。<br />\n因為實際上好難形容比人聽，講左人地又覺得好誇張，令我慢慢唔想同人講&hellip;&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有冇同屋企人講?<br />\n一係睇門診再寫紙轉介睇專科"},{"pid":"f848a9f93bc5957eb05145e6dae377919d35ce9d","tid":195043,"uid":81734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T14:50:56.000Z","msg":"伊藤潤二既長夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我間唔中都有，發完夢訓醒唔肯定有無發生過，好影響情緒，以前有情緒病時影響得更加嚴重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c22e72b0da400c1713951f733dd2efd2a57748d9","tid":195043,"uid":54736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T14:57:36.000Z","msg":"唔可以因為外冷內熱而逃避，你呢啲好明顯都幾大問題，盡快就醫啦"},{"pid":"edcc2c3f46a475924e5fd20862bcc3ac8a328f8a","tid":195043,"uid":50952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T15:10:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我最近呢一年都成日發夢，睡眠質素都好差，訓幾個鍾又醒下，又發夢<br />\n我自己覺得發夢好爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好似有兩次人生咁<br />\n但就愈訓愈少，跟住開始失眠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後睇完中醫後睡眠質素好左好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望樓主有早日好返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我從好細個已經係咁，細細個已經唔覺得快樂，因為都係好恐怖既內容。而家大左更加冇「爽」嘅感覺，有好夢就好似中左六合彩咁，好辛苦。<br />\n因為實際上好難形容比人聽，講左人地又覺得好誇張，令我慢慢唔想同人講&hellip;&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有冇同屋企人講?<br />\n一係睇門診再寫紙轉介睇專科</blockquote><br />\n冇啊，我只係同兩個朋友講過。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n政府專科都等幾耐下，我可能會搵大專生心理輔導員。"},{"pid":"7f2ef52d389ca02d9d57d73764f26b341926771a","tid":195043,"uid":50952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T15:11:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>伊藤潤二既長夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我間唔中都有，發完夢訓醒唔肯定有無發生過，好影響情緒，以前有情緒病時影響得更加嚴重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n伊藤潤二有呢個題材？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我一次夢到有人抓住我，話：「你唔存在」<br />\n個晚醒左天光先訓得番。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"276dd915299fd391bffc01cba41b9372f1f33c9f","tid":195043,"uid":50952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T15:16:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔可以因為外冷內熱而逃避，你呢啲好明顯都幾大問題，盡快就醫啦</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我一直冇睇係以為好多人都係咁&hellip;&hellip;原來<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a37bf830132775aa5db489d8d9cfaf8bf5f65484","tid":195043,"uid":9136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T15:19:38.000Z","msg":"長夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92a70203fa7741089ded006fadb0403368b7a7ab","tid":195043,"uid":50952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T15:22:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>長夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實我冇睇過，我係咪應該去睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a912da44e62805dc7f37b54838917dedb6871120","tid":195043,"uid":79098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T15:22:36.000Z","msg":"要睇醫生加一<br />\nBetween 不如試下寫夢日記<br />\n可能有幫助"},{"pid":"e507ce3323eb90f339da080d59882231934fe568","tid":195043,"uid":81734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T15:52:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>伊藤潤二既長夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我間唔中都有，發完夢訓醒唔肯定有無發生過，好影響情緒，以前有情緒病時影響得更加嚴重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n伊藤潤二有呢個題材？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我一次夢到有人抓住我，話：「你唔存在」<br />\n個晚醒左天光先訓得番。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我啲夢主要係比較寫實所以令我好混淆，樓主你會唔會心理上好多壓抑好多情緒無抒發，搵下醫生/社工傾下可能有幫助"},{"pid":"284b09115ab1dde5b1c52d8eaf289c0b8f9aa1ef","tid":195043,"uid":50952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T15:57:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>要睇醫生加一<br />\nBetween 不如試下寫夢日記<br />\n可能有幫助</blockquote><br />\n好多夢都好可怕，我唔太願意記錄下來"},{"pid":"929a127df86c7089e59fca91d4c4f253d0ce8ae2","tid":195043,"uid":50952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T15:57:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>伊藤潤二既長夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我間唔中都有，發完夢訓醒唔肯定有無發生過，好影響情緒，以前有情緒病時影響得更加嚴重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n伊藤潤二有呢個題材？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我一次夢到有人抓住我，話：「你唔存在」<br />\n個晚醒左天光先訓得番。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我啲夢主要係比較寫實所以令我好混淆，樓主你會唔會心理上好多壓抑好多情緒無抒發，搵下醫生/社工傾下可能有幫助</blockquote><br />\n好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d038c16e8fff018b62d17fe4519af896af62c97a","tid":195043,"uid":83499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T16:01:15.000Z","msg":"可能係多重人格<br />\n細細個既創傷造成 有另一個你想原來既你消滅"},{"pid":"e5264321383b715a1f936afea92e88ba6c8bb4ba","tid":195043,"uid":50952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T16:50:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>可能係多重人格<br />\n細細個既創傷造成 有另一個你想原來既你消滅</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我一諗到呢度手都震震地，當然唔希望真係有另一個人格存在，但如果真係有主人格，咁而家嘅我到底係咩呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81c99363facca7aaf77363610fac7737a10d8c03","tid":195043,"uid":104903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T17:25:49.000Z","msg":"樓主加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不如試下食中藥或者睇睇精神科醫生 咁樣落去都唔係辦法 一直禁辛苦 會影響埋日常既野 唔好乜都唔做 覆加油啊！"},{"pid":"73acd836e6f57ba278d7b4a45d433297d7d0d094","tid":195043,"uid":90248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T17:49:47.000Z","msg":"樓主需要抒發情緒<br />\n<br />\n但適合自己既方法唔係一時三刻搵到，加油<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"beb8fb8de9342fea227623b8ae016b0434d35e84","tid":195043,"uid":32877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T18:37:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>真係要睇 我都會俾夢困擾 不過情況輕微好多好多</blockquote><br />\n巴打睇醫生好番？</blockquote><br />\n我好小事唔洗睇 但覺得你都係睇下好點 因為我無出現過人格被追殺<br />\n或者可以試下現實寫日記？咁起碼分到夢境同現實先"},{"pid":"ab962d3a2af7369a64cb1fc1c3249ddca468930b","tid":195043,"uid":100331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T18:48:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>可能係多重人格<br />\n細細個既創傷造成 有另一個你想原來既你消滅</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我一諗到呢度手都震震地，當然唔希望真係有另一個人格存在，但如果真係有主人格，咁而家嘅我到底係咩呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n而家既你都係你 我係同緊你講緊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但大家都係門外漢 始終比唔到咩實際建議你<br />\n而家最重要都係睇左醫生先<br />\n<br />\n（我明發惡夢個種恐懼 真係唔會想記起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）"},{"pid":"9eebc0241366b5747db3fe208a478fabf450696d","tid":195043,"uid":31777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T19:13:38.000Z","msg":"點解好似睇過，之前有巴打話發夢會去另一個平行時空<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過講番正題。<br />\n塞翁失馬，焉知非福。<br />\n你比起普通人有更加神奇嘅經歷，<br />\n或者係屬於你嘅機遇呢？<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">如果唔係精神方面問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span><br />\n<br />\n我覺得你嘅問題係唔敢面對，<br />\n既然知道係夢，不如抱著博一博嘅諗法<br />\n唔係你死就係我亡<br />\n<br />\n既來之，則安之<br />\n下次再發惡夢，俾多少少勇氣自己<br />\n一次唔得，就兩次，三次，四次<br />\n因為驚只會令自己仲驚<br />\n<br />\n樓主比啲信心自己<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">有危必有機，</span><br />\n令佢化為你嘅機遇咪仲好<br />\n我都無辦法幫到你<br />\n只有靠自己勇敢面對！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e35ad600d436a7ecc6cdf30c3d860861d375bb82","tid":195043,"uid":16650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T19:34:10.000Z","msg":"睇哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇完樓主既經歷，諗起一套動漫<br />\n加速世界，世界入面十幾分鐘會等於現實一年<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n樓主或者試下寫日記，寫下夢中發生既事，同埋夢後現實中自己既變化，因為心理學上有種夢的解析學說"},{"pid":"18787a7e2fa071f2b591c7be6dcc2471aad1052d","tid":195043,"uid":59654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T19:49:04.000Z","msg":"我都有少少似 但無樓主咁誇張<br />\n經常一起身個下覺得自己經歷左好多嘢咁<br />\n發緊夢時次次都好真實 <br />\n無一次知自己發緊夢 <br />\n但我次次個夢都好唔同 唔會連貫<br />\n之後起身個人累到好似未訓過咁<br />\n個腦暈陀陀<br />\n<br />\n之後發覺訓之前會有預感 <br />\n就訓著前個心會好亂 多數就會咁<br />\n就出去睇下電視 平伏下先訓<br />\n就多數無事"},{"pid":"f24eccb047076dd3d1363f6aa968a7e22fa2d7f8","tid":195043,"uid":83016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T20:18:42.000Z","msg":"其實照咁睇你裂嘅機會都好大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你未必係原本嘅人格，但係你有能力成為主導人格，而且如果你原本嘅人格係傾向暴力嘅話，你其實一定要把持住主導權，即使你唔係主人都好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 儘快就醫啦<br />\nbtw 有冇諗過去講故台出文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14b749a4bf83ce61661fa44f3848cfec6b802945","tid":195043,"uid":50952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T04:53:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不如試下食中藥或者睇睇精神科醫生 咁樣落去都唔係辦法 一直禁辛苦 會影響埋日常既野 唔好乜都唔做 覆加油啊！</blockquote><br />\n真係好影響，好似驚緊啲唔存在嘅野，好驚連自我都失去。"},{"pid":"80e0b19c42cf95c52da07c666ba00840f4651a93","tid":195043,"uid":50952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T04:58:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>真係要睇 我都會俾夢困擾 不過情況輕微好多好多</blockquote><br />\n巴打睇醫生好番？</blockquote><br />\n我好小事唔洗睇 但覺得你都係睇下好點 因為我無出現過人格被追殺<br />\n或者可以試下現實寫日記？咁起碼分到夢境同現實先</blockquote><br />\n寫現實嘅日記？好似可以一試<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n隨便夢嘅嚴重性，我可以分得出夢同現實。<br />\n好似前日夢到比「我」追殺，最後我向教授（真係我現實嘅教授）求救，「我」強行拉走我，最後我臨醒時咆哮一句：「我永遠不會放棄！！」<br />\n到底係點解呢..."},{"pid":"2ab23e2328dac90fc82c16e35c4b7788186d1cc7","tid":195043,"uid":50952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T05:04:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>可能係多重人格<br />\n細細個既創傷造成 有另一個你想原來既你消滅</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我一諗到呢度手都震震地，當然唔希望真係有另一個人格存在，但如果真係有主人格，咁而家嘅我到底係咩呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n而家既你都係你 我係同緊你講緊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但大家都係門外漢 始終比唔到咩實際建議你<br />\n而家最重要都係睇左醫生先<br />\n<br />\n（我明發惡夢個種恐懼 真係唔會想記起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）</blockquote><br />\n好，我今日會番學睇下有冇呢方面嘅支援！<br />\n我男朋友都係咁同我講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢話我冇事，我就係我。<br />\n尋晚都響度諗，如果我只係製造出黎，黎逃避一啲主人格唔願意面對嘅嘢，咁代唔代表我唔係本人？<br />\n後來我覺得... 我唔會有。<br />\n我意思係，我唔覺得自己脆弱到要逃避。<br />\nSorry for 1999<br />\n但我相信自己係堅強人！"},{"pid":"66ad910e289a6adefe50ac90f5ece96049203fb2","tid":195043,"uid":85307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T05:07:58.000Z","msg":"好罕有<br />\n建議你睇睇一本書<br />\n叫 <span style=\"color: red;\">夢與意識投射</span><br />\n利申 有少少研究"},{"pid":"e52b80b7c2c982c91fd9c0f8ae77e0b20adc45cf","tid":195043,"uid":37053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T05:13:44.000Z","msg":"啱啱睇完隔離個神祕post再睇到樓主分享，令我好想建議樓主去搵個靈性老師解下夢<br />\n<br />\n但作為讀過下心理學的巴打我都會建議你去搵個臨床心理學家/Counsellor 諮詢下先 (雖然我唔覺得香港有好多人識處理)<br />\n不斷重覆類似的夢好可能係因為童年發生的事未處理好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之前有朋友又係幾乎每晚都發夢夢見被熟人變成鬼/彊屍追殺然後扎醒。後來有位心理學巴問佢細個係咪被屋企某位女性侵犯過之後，佢就好似無再發惡夢了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b96a06f002f5934d64f71056de39c55b0ca4e3eb","tid":195043,"uid":50952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T08:20:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇完樓主既經歷，諗起一套動漫<br />\n加速世界，世界入面十幾分鐘會等於現實一年<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n樓主或者試下寫日記，寫下夢中發生既事，同埋夢後現實中自己既變化，因為心理學上有種夢的解析學說</blockquote><br />\n我反而覺得好似inception （好似係呢個名）<br />\n當年我睇完，人家會話好難明，我係會明個套戲講緊乜，因為我就係咁。雖然冇夢中夢得咁嚴重，兩層對我黎講都幾常見下。<br />\n因為好多夢嘅內容我好抗拒提起，我會講嘅都係我接受到嘅，太痛苦我就唔想講了。"},{"pid":"cf39fc9413505ed21f327c96bd876f4c9e5c372c","tid":195043,"uid":50952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T08:23:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都有少少似 但無樓主咁誇張<br />\n經常一起身個下覺得自己經歷左好多嘢咁<br />\n發緊夢時次次都好真實 <br />\n無一次知自己發緊夢 <br />\n但我次次個夢都好唔同 唔會連貫<br />\n之後起身個人累到好似未訓過咁<br />\n個腦暈陀陀<br />\n<br />\n之後發覺訓之前會有預感 <br />\n就訓著前個心會好亂 多數就會咁<br />\n就出去睇下電視 平伏下先訓<br />\n就多數無事</blockquote><br />\n我係可以好開心去訓都會發惡夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而尋日日頭發生過嘅事，對我黎講已經好遠了，冇左時間嘅概念。"},{"pid":"3c1434184ea9ae1b418f49794ff9e6e58b4a3177","tid":195043,"uid":50952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T08:29:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實照咁睇你裂嘅機會都好大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你未必係原本嘅人格，但係你有能力成為主導人格，而且如果你原本嘅人格係傾向暴力嘅話，你其實一定要把持住主導權，即使你唔係主人都好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 儘快就醫啦<br />\nbtw 有冇諗過去講故台出文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 雖然我覺得我唔係分裂，但我唔敢講到咁實。<br />\n<br />\n我都係一個小作家，而大部分嘅零感都係由夢裡得黎的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但故仔大部分都係科幻+血腥，其實呢個問題都搞到我份人幾扭曲下..."}]}